<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>HTML Headings Example</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Main Heading (H1)</h1>
    <p>This is the main heading of the page.</p>
    
    <h2>Subheading (H2)</h2>
    <p>This is a subheading under the main heading.</p>
    
    <h3>Sub-subheading (H3)</h3>
    <p>This is a sub-subheading under the subheading.</p>
    
    <h4>Lesser Subheading (H4)</h4>
    <p>This is a lesser subheading under the sub-subheading.</p>
    
    <h5>Even Lesser Subheading (H5)</h5>
    <p>This is an even lesser subheading under the lesser subheading.</p>
    
    <h6>Least Important Subheading (H6)</h6>
    <p>This is the least important subheading under the even lesser subheading.</p>
</body>
</html>
